@startuml
title Smart Data Discovery (RAG Flow)

actor User
participant "Telegram API" as TelegramAPI
participant "Telegram Controller" as TelegramCtrl
participant "Orchestrator" as Orchestrator
participant "AI Service" as AIService
participant "Knowledge Service (RAG)" as KnowledgeService
participant "Vector Store Adapter" as VectorAdapter
participant "Vector Store" as VectorDB
participant "LLM Adapter" as LlmAdapter
participant "LLM" as LLM

User -> TelegramAPI: sends message
TelegramAPI -> TelegramCtrl: receive message
TelegramCtrl -> Orchestrator: handle message
Orchestrator -> AIService: process user query
AIService -> KnowledgeService: search relevant data
KnowledgeService -> VectorAdapter: query vector store
VectorAdapter -> VectorDB: retrieve embeddings
VectorDB --> VectorAdapter: return results
VectorAdapter --> KnowledgeService: results
KnowledgeService --> AIService: relevant data
AIService -> LlmAdapter: generate natural response
LlmAdapter -> LLM: call LLM API
LLM --> LlmAdapter: return response
LlmAdapter --> AIService: response
AIService --> Orchestrator: final message
Orchestrator --> TelegramCtrl: send message
TelegramCtrl -> TelegramAPI: deliver message
TelegramAPI --> User: display response
@enduml
